snippet.title: Amber Heard Faces YEARS Of JAIL TIME (Official Update)
snippet.description:
🖤 Amber Heard Faces YEARS Of JAIL TIME (Official) 
Amber Heard and her friend Rocky Pennington stages the 21st May crime scene to prove the abuse allegations against Johnny Depp. Well, how can someone go so down to prove someone wrong, even when he is not? If you have been following the Amber Heard and Johnny Depp domestic abuse case since day one, you undoubtedly know that the situation seems to grow even more contentious.
After the Caribbean Pirates, Johnny Depp lost his right to appeal his libel case loss in London. The LAPD - Los Angeles Police Department body cam, the footage surfaced indicating that Amber Heard might not have been truthful in her domestic violence allegations.
